<i>Hampstead Heath,
Hampstead Heath,</i>


321
0:23:10,88 --> 0:23:13,56
<i>Close to the meat, Hampstead Heath,</i>


322
0:23:13,56 --> 0:23:19,0
<i>He roams wild on Hampstead Heath,
Hampstead Heath,</i>


323
0:23:19,0 --> 0:23:21,12
Hello ?


324
0:23:21,12 --> 0:23:25,16
Is anyone there ?


325
0:23:25,16 --> 0:23:34,4
I can assure you,
this isn't the least bit amusing.


